item.dc:creator: @hasumon hasumon
item.description:
@hasumon wrote:

could be a couple of problems

1.) Blocked program as in you didnt set your computer to trust the publisher ( Java )
2.) Didnt download Java which seems very unlikely
3.) Download of page rate timed out.
4.) You canceled the loading.
5.) Your internet is acting up.
6.) Virus -.-
7.) Your computer sucks
